sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist<br/>(Jupyter Notebook)
    participant SDK as CodeFlare SDK
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant KubeRay as KubeRay Operator
    participant RayHead as Ray Head Node<br/>(head-svc)
    participant Dashboard as Ray Dashboard<br/>443/TCP HTTPS (via HTTPRoute)
    participant RayClient as Ray Client Port<br/>10001/TCP gRPC mTLS

    Note over User,RayClient: Flow 1: Create and Connect to a Ray Cluster

    User->>SDK: Cluster(config).apply()
    SDK->>K8sAPI: POST RayCluster CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>SDK: RayCluster created
    KubeRay->>KubeRay: Reconcile → create Ray head/worker pods

    loop Poll cluster status
        SDK->>K8sAPI: GET RayCluster status<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI-->>SDK: Status (pending/ready)
    end

    SDK->>K8sAPI: GET Secret (CA cert)<br/>ray.openshift.ai/cluster-name label
    K8sAPI-->>SDK: CA certificate + key
    SDK->>SDK: Generate client TLS certs<br/>RSA 3072-bit, SHA-256<br/>Write to ~/.local/share/codeflare/tls/

    SDK->>K8sAPI: GET HTTPRoute / Route / Ingress<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>SDK: Dashboard URL

    SDK->>Dashboard: GET dashboard readiness<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Dashboard-->>SDK: Dashboard ready

    SDK->>RayClient: ray.init() gRPC connection<br/>Auth: Client mTLS certificate
    RayClient-->>SDK: Connected

    Note over User,RayClient: Flow 2: Submit a RayJob

    User->>SDK: RayJobClient(config).submit()
    SDK->>K8sAPI: POST Secret ({job}-files)<br/>Local files + working_dir zip<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>SDK: Secret created
    SDK->>K8sAPI: POST RayJob CR<br/>(with ownerRef to files Secret)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>SDK: RayJob created
    KubeRay->>KubeRay: Reconcile → create submitter pod

    loop Poll job status
        SDK->>K8sAPI: GET RayJob status<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI-->>SDK: Status (running/succeeded/failed)
    end

    Note over User,RayClient: Flow 3: Kueue Queue Management

    User->>SDK: list_local_queues()
    SDK->>K8sAPI: GET LocalQueues<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>SDK: LocalQueue list
    SDK->>K8sAPI: GET Workloads (queue status)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>SDK: Workload admission status
    SDK->>SDK: Add kueue.x-k8s.io/queue-name<br/>label to RayCluster/RayJob CR
